Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.11,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.65,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.44,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.37,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:11.86,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:17.76,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:20.81,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,has been verified,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:24.20,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:30.26,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:35.60,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:37.99,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:44.54,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.33,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:56.59,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:02:01.49,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.80,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered\Njust before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around\Nthe world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered\Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago,\Neverything was taken away from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and many people's lives\Nwere ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was caused by a single attack--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...targeted on the friends I was finally\Nable to find, whom I can be myself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I wish to be with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more my fate\Nwill show its fangs to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I go on the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a huge enemy\Nthat I can't shake off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the world and\Nits darkness are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident with Aokiji,\Nas well as this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already dragged you\Ninto my troubles twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this continues forever, even though\Nyou guys're good-natured...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll eventually feel\Nthat I'm a burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll betray me\None day and abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm most afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want\Nyou to come to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to die someday anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die\Nright here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That indeed is a sound argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is stupid enough\Nto think that having you isn't a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that symbol,\Nyou damn pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That logo indicates the unity\Nof over 170 member countries
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spanning the four seas\Nand the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you now realize how completely\Npowerless you guys are to fight against it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how huge\Nof an organization
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this woman has been pursued by?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now understand well the\Nidentity of Robin's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot through that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new weapon,\Na huge slingshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,named Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good look at its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack... Firebird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They've gone and done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they understand what it\Nmeans to attack the flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates declared war\Nagainst the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that\Nyou'll be able to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after making the entire\Nworld your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't heard you say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something\NI dared not wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever let me wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is vast,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends\Nwho'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's really okay for me\Nto utter my wish for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the sea with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...!\NI love you guys, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm Not Gonna Hand over\Nthe Blueprints! Franky's Decision"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We pulled the lever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Mozu and the\Nothers did okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they pulled through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm trembling with anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower that bridge already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that they don't fear\Nthe flag of the Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way\Nthat they could defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare those damn pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the trench mortar ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the drawbridge!\NBreak it if you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe Hitch Knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demolition Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Justice Baskerville!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually\Nthe Chief Justice trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the Left Baskerville,\Nam named Bas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the Right Baskerville,\Nam named Kerville!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, the Center Baskerville,\Ngo by the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those three were just\Nsticking together? That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the trench mortar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge\Nstopped coming down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they get in our way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Spandam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please evacuate\Nfrom the Tower of Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head to the Gates of Justice\Nbefore they come over to this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Bring Cutty Flam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those pirates are just nobodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the assassin group\NCP9 on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin, a survivor\Nof the island of scholars
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who schemed to bring back\Nthe weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam, who inherited\Nthe weapon's blueprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely not gonna stand back and\Nmiss this opportunity to gain big power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those are the ancient\Nweapon Pluton's blueprints...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci... Kaku...\NYou guys can tell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was unlikely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were hiding them\Ninside your body, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The real ones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the real ones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand them over...\NHand them over to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my long-sought\Nblueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors are such unreliable things,\Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were being\Nbrought to this damn place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to realize\Nthat you aren't the evil
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's trying to misuse the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to build the weapon isn't\Nwhat the Water Seven's shipwrights
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been inheriting for\Ngenerations in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san achieved\Nso many great things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he gave up everything in order to\Npreserve these blueprints for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, as long as there's a risk
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a woman named Nico Robin\Ncan restore the weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the world needs\Nthose blueprints to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Spanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Tom-san and Iceberg\Nrisked their lives to protect is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand them over to me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the wish of this\Nweapon's architect--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is, if the ancient weapon fell\Ninto the hands of an idiot like you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and started being used\Nto cause trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would want another weapon\Nto be built in order to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that if you use Nico Robin,\Nyou can revive the ancient weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she doesn't\Nwant to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as there's a chance\Nthat she could be used,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's still dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's got friends
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who would be willing to risk\Ntheir lives to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of only one way that I could\Nuphold the architect's wish in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and hand them\Nover to me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:14:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation,\NI'm sure you'd also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of only one way that I could\Nuphold the architect's wish in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and hand them\Nover to me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation,\NI'm sure you'd also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's burned black!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our five-year mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blueprints were kept in order\Nto create a weapon to fight back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, the Government,\Ncame after them a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Essentially, something like\Nthis should remain a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so once it's revealed,\Nit has to be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there's no longer power to\Nfight back against the ancient weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done and Nico Robin\Nfalls into your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the Straw Hats win...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there won't be anything\Nleft to you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a bet on their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you mock me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you want\Nto die here, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro is at the Tower of Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! He's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came with the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodom and Gomorrah\Nfought hard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who asked you to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come rescue me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards! I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up\Nand bring down the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, you guys!\NOr I'm gonna beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you when you're contradictory\Nlike that, too, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you helped\Nmy underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, their boss, the great Franky,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will add my super fighting power\Nto you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still holding what\Nyou did to Usopp against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... well,\Nhe's right next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...burn my blueprints?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro is falling into the falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kokoro-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys wasting time for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the\Nbridge is only halfway down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway is good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there in four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump with all your might\Ntowards the falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... from earlier...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she said\Njump towards the falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A sea train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it coming into the courthouse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney, sound the\Nwhistle with gusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocketman can still run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate Tom's Workers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a legendary ship-building company!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rocketman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories,\Ndoesn't it, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About assisting that Roger guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm resolutely proud of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man\Nwho'll be King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was an idiot like him,\Ntoo, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you helped him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like we didn't learn our lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Tom's Workers\Nis helping this pirate kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would've done the same,\Nwouldn't you, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna collide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands,\NRobin will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something before\Nthey go through the Gates of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means we have to defeat\NCP9 and get those five keys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we don't\Nhave much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Take them down\Neven if it costs you your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.05,0:23:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.62,0:23:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Obtain the Five Keys!\NThe Straw Hat Pirates vs. CP9"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
